# --- Shared defaults (all modes) ---
# Optional — patient/practitioner SPA (“Back to clinic site” on login)
# VITE_MAIN_APP_URL=http://127.0.0.1:5173

# --- `npm run dev` (mode: development) ---
# Copy this file to `.env` if you have no other env file yet.
# `.env.development` in the repo points the admin dev server at the hosted API (see below).
# To use a **local** backend + Vite proxy instead, create `.env.development.local` (gitignored) with:
#   VITE_API_BASE_URL=/api/v1
#   VITE_APP_URL=http://127.0.0.1:5174

# --- `vite build` / production (mode: production) ---
# Values live in `.env.production` (same pattern as mrdonlineclinic-web).
# Note: `.env.production` is NOT loaded during `npm run dev` — only during build.
